        {
          "text": "The following is a recording of an interview conducted by Mel Gussow Sept. 25, 2000 with Margaret Atwood. Mel Gussow was the lead cultural critic for "
        },
        {
          "text": "The New York Times",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": " for over 40 years (1969-2005), becoming an important figure in both American and British culture. According to the Harry Ransom Center, \"This remarkable collection captures a broad range of 40 years of literary and theatrical achievement through the voices of the people who made it.\" You can see more of his recordings "
        },
        {
          "text": "here",
          "link": "https://hrc.contentdm.oclc.org/digital/collection/p15878coll83"
        },
        {
          "text": "."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
